"pokemon_desc_0670_0002", "This rare Floette holds a plant that died out in ancient times. The Pokémon is said to harbor an incredible power.",
"pokemon_desc_0778_busted", "정체를 들킬 것 같아 슬퍼한다. 목 부분을 꺾은 상대는 절대 용서하지 않고 복수한다.",
"pokemon_desc_0999_0002", "This Pokémon was born inside a treasure chest about 1,500 years ago. It sucks the life-force out of scoundrels who try to steal the treasure.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0026_0001", "It resembles an X as it flies through the air with 50 million volts of electricity sparking from its ears and forked tail.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0026_0002", "It fires bolts of electricity from the tip of its tail and from the spiky tufts of fur growing out of its temples. This electricity forms the letter Y.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0358_0001", "It vibrates its entire body to attack in all directions using sound waves. Any who hear the vibrations get so confused, they forget who they are.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0359_0002", "Using fur that it has made into sharp, clawlike shapes, it cuts down foes with a single blow. This is an act of kindness to keep them from suffering.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0398_0001", "Mega Staraptor is a top-class flier. It can easily soar through the sky while gripping a Steelix that weighs more than 880 lbs.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0448_0002", "By completely cloaking itself in its aura, Mega Lucario Z can parry all manner of attacks, battling as if it were gracefully dancing.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0485_0001", "It’s said that if it goes all out, it can heat its body up to temperatures over 1.8 million degrees Fahrenheit. This heat keeps enemies at bay.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0491_0001", "Its dark power blocks out the sun, plunging the surrounding area into darkness. There is no escaping its evil eye.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0530_0001", "If this Pokémon brings its arms and head together to form a streamlined shape and spins at high speeds, it can destroy anything.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0623_0001", "The energy within Golurk has been stimulated by Mega Evolution. The Pokémon could explode at any moment.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0670_0001", "The Eternal Flower has absorbed all the energy from Mega Evolution. The flower now attacks enemies on its own.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0678_0001", "Mega Meowstic can use its psychic power to compress or expand anything. It overwhelms foes by contorting space itself.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0740_0001", "It can pulverize reinforced concrete with a light swing of one of its fists, each of which is covered in a thick layer of ice.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0768_0001", "It uses four of its arms to fiercely assail its foes. Once they’ve been pushed to the brink of defeat, it finishes them off with the arms it kept hidden.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0801_0001", "This is Magearna once a previously hidden mode activates. The emotions Magearna had begun to feel now hide away as it fells foe after foe.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0807_0001", "It stores up 10 lightning strikes’ worth of electricity. When it stops limiting itself, it’s in the strongest class of electric Pokémon.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0952_0001", "Mega Evolution has dialed up this Pokémon’s spiciness. It swings its “necktie” around to wallop its foes.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0970_0001", "Glimmora’s petals—now larger and separated from its main body—rotate around it to provide defense while scattering poisonous fragments.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0978_0001_01", "Tatsugiri’s brain has been invigorated by Mega Evolution, making it even wilier. It can create and command copies of itself.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0978_0001_02", "It solidifies the energy of Mega Evolution, building up an overflowing pile to launch as projectiles. These projectiles explode on contact.",
"pokemon_desc_tmpevo_0978_0001_03", "Using the energy of Mega Evolution, it creates a dish to ride upon, allowing it to move with total freedom—even through the air.",
"pokemon_ibfc_desc_0778", "배틀 중 1번만 스페셜 어택을 방어합니다. 배틀 종료시까지 따라큐의 방어가 떨어집니다.",
